Our Midtown Manhattan location and a <a href="https://www.ilr.cornell.edu/programs/graduate-degree-programs/mps-program-new-york-city/academics-curriculum/program-structure?utm_source=ub-followup&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=sp19">part-time schedule</a> designed to complement the demands of your busy work life mean you can earn your master’s from Cornell in just 21 months, without interrupting your career.<br><br>
